{
  "id": "652c4cb6d0f263001b8c62e2",
  "title": "確率1/Nのくじを何回引くと何%で当たるか",
  "created": 1697402039,
  "updated": 1697616684,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "652c4cb6d0f263001b8c62e2",
      "text": "確率1/Nのくじを何回引くと何%で当たるか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402039,
      "updated": 1697402039
    },
    {
      "id": "652c4cb7ed60e60000c76a37",
      "text": "from [2023/10/07]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402039,
      "updated": 1697402039
    },
    {
      "id": "652c4cb7ed60e60000c76a38",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402039,
      "updated": 1697402044
    },
    {
      "id": "652c4cb7ed60e60000c76a39",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402039,
      "updated": 1697402039
    },
    {
      "id": "652c4cb7ed60e60000c76a3a",
      "text": " [火竜の天鱗]を引くまでの[リオレウス]の屍の数を見積もるために自力で[ポワソン分布]らしきものを導出したことがある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402039,
      "updated": 1697402039
    },
    {
      "id": "652c4cb7ed60e60000c76a3b",
      "text": " \t後に確率の授業で[ポワソン分布]というものを知った",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402039,
      "updated": 1697402039
    },
    {
      "id": "652c4cb7ed60e60000c76a3c",
      "text": " \t知らずに自力で導出すると「こんなところに[$ e]が！」と感動する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402039,
      "updated": 1697402039
    },
    {
      "id": "652c4cdbed60e60000c76a41",
      "text": " \t\t[知らずに自力で導出すると感動する]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402076,
      "updated": 1697402088
    },
    {
      "id": "652c4cb7ed60e60000c76a3d",
      "text": " \t思い出してきた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402039,
      "updated": 1697402039
    },
    {
      "id": "652c4cb7ed60e60000c76a3e",
      "text": " \t\t[$ \\frac1N ]のくじであたりを引くまでの回数は[$ 4.5N ]くらいにすると大体[$ 99[\\%] ]の確率で当たりが引けるみたいな公式を作ってた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402039,
      "updated": 1697402039
    },
    {
      "id": "652c4cb7ed60e60000c76a3f",
      "text": " \t\t\t実際は[$ N ]回引けば[$ 63[\\%] ]の確率で当たるの方でチャレンジして、当たらなかったら慰めのために[$ 4.5N]の方を思い出す",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402039,
      "updated": 1697402039
    },
    {
      "id": "652c4cb7ed60e60000c76a40",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697402039,
      "updated": 1697402039
    },
    {
      "id": "652dd8f8aff09e0000df5c3e",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697503480,
      "updated": 1697503482
    },
    {
      "id": "652dd8faaff09e0000df5c40",
      "text": " 1%で当たるくじを",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697503483,
      "updated": 1697503501
    },
    {
      "id": "652dd90caff09e0000df5c41",
      "text": " 　A: 当たるまで引く場合の引く回数の期待値",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697503501,
      "updated": 1697503521
    },
    {
      "id": "652dd921aff09e0000df5c42",
      "text": " 　B: 100回引いた時の当たる確率",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697503521,
      "updated": 1697503541
    },
    {
      "id": "652dd93aaff09e0000df5c43",
      "text": " 　C: 100回引いた時の当たる回数の期待値",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697503546,
      "updated": 1697503574
    },
    {
      "id": "652dd956aff09e0000df5c44",
      "text": " の関係ってあんまり自明じゃないよね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697503575,
      "updated": 1697503583
    },
    {
      "id": "652dd8faaff09e0000df5c3f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697503482,
      "updated": 1697503482
    },
    {
      "id": "652e79f1ed60e600005d6509",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697544689,
      "updated": 1697544692
    },
    {
      "id": "652e79f4ed60e600005d650a",
      "text": "\tある程度小さい確率[$ \\frac1n]で当たるくじの[\" [nishio.icon]]の諸々を求めたい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697544692,
      "updated": 1697545685
    },
    {
      "id": "652e7dc4ed60e600005d650f",
      "text": "\t\tA: 当たるまで引く場合の引く回数の期待値",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697545669,
      "updated": 1697599078
    },
    {
      "id": "652e7a15ed60e600005d650c",
      "text": "\t\tB: [$ n]回引いたときの当たり確率",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697544725,
      "updated": 1697545690
    },
    {
      "id": "652e7a7bed60e600005d650d",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ \\left(1-\\frac{1}{n}\\right)^n=\\frac1{\\left(1+\\frac1{n-1}\\right)^{n-1}\\cdot(1+\\frac1{n-1})}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697544827,
      "updated": 1697545781
    },
    {
      "id": "652e7b9fed60e600005d650e",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ >\\frac1e]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697545120,
      "updated": 1697545870
    },
    {
      "id": "652e8272ed60e600005d6513",
      "text": "\t\tC: [$ n]回引いたときの当たる回数の期待値",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697546867,
      "updated": 1697546867
    },
    {
      "id": "652e7edaed60e600005d6511",
      "text": "\t👀[https://bellcurve.jp/statistics/course/6988.html 13-5. 幾何分布 | 統計学の時間 | 統計WEB]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697545946,
      "updated": 1697547992
    },
    {
      "id": "652e86d7ed60e600005d6515",
      "text": " 👀[https://bellcurve.jp/statistics/course/24550.html 13-7. 超幾何分布 | 統計学の時間 | 統計WEB]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697547992,
      "updated": 1697548019
    },
    {
      "id": "652f4e8ded60e6000060dcf1",
      "text": " 特殊事例よりも一般的に確率[$ \\frac{K}{N}]のくじの諸々を求めることで各種確率分布を導くほうが楽しそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697599117,
      "updated": 1697599167
    },
    {
      "id": "652f4ed6ed60e6000060dcf2",
      "text": " \tちゃんと確率を教えるところではこれをやると思う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697599191,
      "updated": 1697599206
    },
    {
      "id": "652f4f29ed60e6000060dcf3",
      "text": " \t1. [$ n]回引いて[$ k]回当たる確率",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697599274,
      "updated": 1697613994
    },
    {
      "id": "652f4f46ed60e6000060dcf4",
      "text": " \t\t[$ _nC_k\\left(\\frac KN\\right)^k\\left(1-\\frac KN\\right)^{n-k}]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697599302,
      "updated": 1697614901
    },
    {
      "id": "652f8c35ed60e600002b24ee",
      "text": "  \t\t[$ =\\,_nC_kp^k(1-p)^{n-k}\\quad\\left(p=\\frac{K}{N}\\right)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697614901,
      "updated": 1697614926
    },
    {
      "id": "652f919eed60e600002b24f4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1697616286,
      "updated": 1697616647
    },
    {
      "id": "652f633aaff09e00009e9bac",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697604410,
      "updated": 1697604424
    },
    {
      "id": "652f6348aff09e00009e9bad",
      "text": "\tA:  1%で当たるくじを当たるまで引く場合の引く回数の期待値",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697604425,
      "updated": 1697604901
    },
    {
      "id": "652f6511aff09e00009e9bb2",
      "text": "\t\t[$ E = 1 \\times {1\\over 100} + 2 \\times {99 \\over 100} \\times {1\\over 100} + 3 \\times {99 \\over 100} \\times {99 \\over 100} \\times {1\\over 100} + \\ldots]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697604882,
      "updated": 1697604888
    },
    {
      "id": "652f634caff09e00009e9bae",
      "text": "\t\tこのn項までの和をSnとした場合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697604428,
      "updated": 1697604738
    },
    {
      "id": "652f6481aff09e00009e9bb0",
      "text": "\t\t[$ Sn - {99 \\over 100} Sn = 1 \\times {1\\over 100} + 1 \\times {99 \\over 100} \\times {1\\over 100} + 1 \\times {99 \\over 100} \\times {99 \\over 100} \\times {1\\over 100} + \\ldots] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697604738,
      "updated": 1697604785
    },
    {
      "id": "652f646aaff09e00009e9baf",
      "text": "\t\tとなって[$ n\\to \\infty]で1になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697604715,
      "updated": 1697604842
    },
    {
      "id": "652f64c5aff09e00009e9bb1",
      "text": "\t\tよって[$ E = 100]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697604806,
      "updated": 1697604895
    },
    {
      "id": "652f651baff09e00009e9bb4",
      "text": "\tC: 1%で当たるくじを100回引いた時の当たる回数の期待値",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697604891,
      "updated": 1697604952
    },
    {
      "id": "652f65b4aff09e00009e9bb8",
      "text": "\t\t1回引いた時の当たる回数の期待値が[$ E_1 = 1 \\times {1\\over 100} + 0 \\times {99 \\over 100} = {1 \\over 100}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697605045,
      "updated": 1697605106
    },
    {
      "id": "652f654aaff09e00009e9bb7",
      "text": "\t\t各試行は独立なので「和の期待値は期待値の和」が成立して[$ E = 1]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697604938,
      "updated": 1697605173
    },
    {
      "id": "652f6613aff09e000051cf43",
      "text": "\tではなぜBが1にならないかというと",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697605139,
      "updated": 1697605231
    },
    {
      "id": "652f66f2aff09e00009e9bbc",
      "text": "\t\tCは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697605363,
      "updated": 1697605367
    },
    {
      "id": "652f66fbaff09e00009e9bbd",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ 0\\times P(X=0) + 1 \\times P(X = 1) + 2 \\times P(X = 2) + \\ldots = 1]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697605372,
      "updated": 1697605372
    },
    {
      "id": "652f6674aff09e00009e9bba",
      "text": "\t\tと言っていて、もちろん",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697605237,
      "updated": 1697605389
    },
    {
      "id": "652f6701aff09e00009e9bbf",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ P(X=0) + P(X = 1) + P(X = 2) + \\ldots = 1]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697605378,
      "updated": 1697605389
    },
    {
      "id": "652f672eaff09e00009e9bc0",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ P(X = 2) + \\ldots > 0]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697605423,
      "updated": 1697605432
    },
    {
      "id": "652f66fdaff09e00009e9bbe",
      "text": "\t\tなのでB、つまり",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697605374,
      "updated": 1697605454
    },
    {
      "id": "652f66b3aff09e00009e9bbb",
      "text": "   [$ P(X = 1) + P(X = 2) + \\ldots]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697605300,
      "updated": 1697605466
    },
    {
      "id": "652f6758aff09e00009e9bc1",
      "text": "\t\tは1になれないというわけ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697605464,
      "updated": 1697605482
    },
    {
      "id": "652f675caff09e00009e9bc2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1697605469,
      "updated": 1697605469
    }
  ]
}